{"tid":584123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港電子支付調查報告！結果會嚇大家一跳","createTime":"2018-03-07T14:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T06:43:50.000Z","uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"60e97685be6adf8da6e92b454b81372b0d5abf41","tid":584123,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:56:25.000Z","msg":"香港雖然常說是國際都會，但電子支付服務還只算是剛剛起步，或許大家會認為會較鄰近地區及國家緩慢，最近一間市場調查公司 J.D. Power，發表一份有關香港電子支付的報告，當中得出的結果，可能會令大家有點意外。<br />\n<br />\n報告指有 52% 的銀行帳戶，經常使用電子支付平台消費，比率上較新加坡及澳洲的 35% 及 19% 為高，但還是比不上中國達 98%，接近全國都用電子支付消費的比率。<br />\n<br />\n而香港最多人用的電子支付平台為 Apple Pay 佔 29%、緊接著的是八達通 O! ePay 17%、Android Pay 16%、Alipay 15% 及 WeChat Pay 8%。至於用家的滿意度來看，滿意評分最高竟然是 WeChat Pay 為 7.7 分，最多人用的 Apple Pay 則為 7.6 分排在次席。<br />\n<br />\n從報告可見，只有 52% 銀行帳戶使用的香港的電子支付市場，現在還在搶市場佔有率為主，發有極大的發展空間，加上去年才加入的 Samsung Pay 應該會在今年發力，估計亦會為用家推出更多優惠，希望大家試用旗下服務。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：jdpower <a href=\"http://www.jdpower.com/press-releases/2018-hong-kong-retail-banking-satisfaction-study\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jdpower.com%2Fpress-releases%2F2018-hong-kong-retail-banking-satisfaction-study&d=fCaBwbOXOM5hpPmwtkDIYqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=1698c1de\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jdpower.com/press-releases/2018-hong-kong-retail-banking-satisfaction-study</a>"},{"pid":"781cd31b41f0d9d09dddb242e09508699988e8dd","tid":584123,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:59:36.000Z","msg":"新加坡辣殺"},{"pid":"4dd22d5d96450c386969c84cd64589e70f82682f","tid":584123,"uid":173233,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:38:15.000Z","msg":"原來apple pay重低分過wechat pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db2f36f680ee90be0d2b12bb811f097e64c441d8","tid":584123,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dd22d5d96450c386969c84cd64589e70f82682f","tid":584123,"uid":173233,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:38:15.000Z","msg":"原來apple pay重低分過wechat pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:40:29.000Z","msg":"8%打手俾分高過29%正常人有咩出奇"},{"pid":"57b810e44c220fdc140074ca3a678849bffa826a","tid":584123,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:46:39.000Z","msg":"如果計左八達通,其實應該市佔超高"},{"pid":"8dae78d3787f20767a555e6bf771415793a84776","tid":584123,"uid":42945,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4dd22d5d96450c386969c84cd64589e70f82682f","tid":584123,"uid":173233,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:38:15.000Z","msg":"原來apple pay重低分過wechat pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:49:06.000Z","msg":"正常呀 ， 用android 機同Apple 都可以用WeChat pay, 但用 android 用唔到 Apple Pay ."},{"pid":"2412a32f46e0f6d0bd14db4a7488e3b2f2590ccd","tid":584123,"uid":153811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1412d6076556f57ecc52111d6a2d2132c582b2f","tid":584123,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2412a32f46e0f6d0bd14db4a7488e3b2f2590ccd","tid":584123,"uid":153811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411e010920dd5024fdf4d51c13c18e5438ed8e8b","tid":584123,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:43:50.000Z","msg":"新加坡同澳洲好落後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}